name: Untitled DR-01
description:
v4w.enko - "Untitled DR-01"
This is procedural sound I made with my custom instrument - node based synthesizer I created by myself with custom coding in the software of Max/Msp. It is a combination of generative "golden ratio" based sequencer, additive synthesis and some tricks with realtime rhythmic structure.  I use such a system to generate all my sound to my audiovisual works. Recorded in realtime from the live algorithm. The composition seems to be a rithmic sound. Have a nice listening / using / mixing  process.  No sound effects are used. Pure wave physics.  Microsound.
